cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE 

This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it presents a new dataset for event-based vision research. The paper also discusses image reconstruction methods for downstream vision applications, which further supports the likelihood of it belonging to the computer vision sub-category. Additionally, the use of event cameras in robotics (cs.RO) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE) may also be relevant to this work.
